Achievements.Name: Demolitionist
Achievements.Description: Blow up the tunnel and airlock at CURSED STATION.

Achievements.Name: DJ Artyom
Achievements.Description: On the level OUTPOST reach the radio tower and broadcast the commander's message.

Achievements.Name: Generous
Achievements.Description: Help the poor, a coin for the kid, medicine for the sick. You help everyone you see.

Achievements.Name: Hedge-hopper
Achievements.Description: On the level FRONTLINE kill all of the enemy Red Army and Fascist Soldiers.

Achievements.Name: Invisible man
Achievements.Description: Complete FRONTLINE level without killing anyone.

Achievements.Name: Manhattan Project
Achievements.Description: Spend 60 seconds in a Radiation Hotspot.

Achievements.Name: Merciful
Achievements.Description: Complete the level BLACK STATION without killing or knocking out any enemies.

Achievements.Name: Blogger
Achievements.Description: Complete all 51 of Artyom's hidden Diary pages.

Achievements.Name: Quick Draw
Achievements.Description: On the level HUNTER kill the nosalises before they break through the ventilation grilles.

Achievements.Name: Raider
Achievements.Description: On the level DEPOT silently kill the first guard and break into the Fascist station unnoticed.

Achievements.Name: Ranger
Achievements.Description: Find all Ranger stashes in Dead City.

Achievements.Name: Rescue Ranger
Achievements.Description: Save a group of Reds from Fascist captivity.

Achievements.Name: Slice & Dice
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 human enemies in close combat.

Achievements.Name: Marksman
Achievements.Description: Kill 15 human enemies with Headshots from at least 30 meters' distance.

Achievements.Name: Spartan 2033
Achievements.Description: Complete the game in Spartan Mode.

Achievements.Name: Stunning
Achievements.Description: Knock 30 human enemies out in close combat.

Achievements.Name: Survivor 2033
Achievements.Description: Complete the game in Survival Mode.

Achievements.Name: Tank
Achievements.Description: Kill 10 Enemies without taking any damage.

Achievements.Name: If it's hostile, you kill it.
Weaponsmith
Achievements.Description: Kill at least one enemy with each weapon available in the game

Achievements.Name: Wheeler-Dealer
Achievements.Description: Exchange 500 Military-Grade 5.45 rounds at Exchange kiosks.
